title: From the Art Ethical Handicrafts and Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, International, Organic, Western, Take-out, Fusion, Middle Eastern
description: Vegetarian cafe and handicraft store. Serves fair trade organic tea and coffee, and makes food in-house. The cafe employs asylum seekers/refugees. It's a social enterprise which helps to support a community in need. Sells hand-crafted items which support disadvantaged communities from around the world to be economically independent.
